  <name>SmartGit</name>
  <summary>Get your commit done</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      SmartGit is a graphical Git and Mercurial client which can also connect to SVN repositories. SmartGit runs on
      Linux, Mac OS X (10.11 or newer) and Windows (7 or newer) with the same intuitive user interface.
    </p>
    <p>
      SmartGit comes with special integrations for GitHub, BitBucket and BitBucket Server (former Atlassian Stash) to
      create and resolve Pull Requests and Review Comments. Of course, you can use SmartGit like any other Git client
      with your own Git repositories or other hosting providers (e.g. GitLab).
    </p>
    <p>
      Find out more on <a href="https://www.syntevo.com/smartgit/purchase/" target="_blank">https://www.syntevo.com/smartgit/purchase/</a>
    </p>
